      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unparalleled opportunity to acquire a vehicle maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen remains in pristine showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously preserved interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been subjected to rigorous inspection to ensure peak performance, reflecting a history of uncompromising care. For the discerning enthusiast seeking a vehicle that transcends the typical secondary market offering, this remains the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
