    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total beauty. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this ride from day one, keeping it waxed, polished, and serviced right on schedule. You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s ready for its next adventure, so come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
